data.data: Here at ACM@CMU, we're proud of everything we do, and that is only possible with our amazing board members. Get to know our team.
Hi there, I'm Jasmine! I'm a senior studying Computer Science and Robotics. When I'm not in the Robotics Education Lab, you can find me at a thrift store, biking around Pittsburgh, or painting.
I’m Maxine and I’m a 2nd year studying Comp Sci! I like eating pan fried dumplings and making jokes. For example, what’d they call a cow with no udders? An udder failure!

Hi! I'm Michelle, a sophomore studying CS and doing research in Comp Bio. I enjoy a wide variety of activities in my free time, like sleeping, eating and sitting. In the future I'd like to remove all snakes (the animal).

Hi! My name is Elaine, and I am a sophomore studying Electrical and Computer Engineering. In my free time, I like to watch tv shows, crochet, and making matcha lattes. I also really enjoy finding good music and my boba order is a honey lemon green tea with lychee jelly.

Hiya, I'm Isaac, and I'm a sophomore studying CS. As of now, I spend most of my time suffering in 251 but I usually spend the rest of my time hanging out / sleeping / going to church / playing fighting games.
Hi! My name is Katie, and I am a sophomore studying Economics and Statistics. In my free time, I enjoy reading, drawing, catching up on sleep, and trying new food.
Hi there! My name is David, and I'm a sophomore studying CS. Outside of school, my favorite hobby is golfing, and I am a member of CMU's men's golf team.
Hello! I'm Jocelyn, a sophomore studying Computer Science and doing research in Augmented Reality! At a given point in time, you can find me in Gates, sleeping, running outdoors, or eating spaghetti.
Hello there, I'm Howard and I am a sophomore studying Math and CS. I enjoying leaving random art on whiteboards around campus and eating General Tso's chicken at Hunan Express.
